OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774951543
OL,3,CPolice begin murder investigation as
OL,4,Cyoung women found dead on suburban
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FDetectives have begun a murder
OL,8,Finvestigation after a young woman was
OL,9,Ffound dead on a Leeds street.
OL,11,FPolice were called just before 6am on
OL,12,FSaturday 28 March to reports that a
OL,13,Fyoung woman had been found unconscious
OL,14,Fon Kennerleigh Avenue, Austhorpe.
OL,16,FShe was found to have suffered serious
OL,17,Finjuries and was taken to hospital for
OL,18,Fmedical treatment, but was pronounced
OL,19,Fdead shortly afterwards.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
