CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774951543
OL,3,CPolice begin murder investigation as
OL,4,Cyoung women found dead on suburban
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FA West Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "The female victim remains
OL,9,Funidentified at this time. Extensive
OL,10,Fenquiries are ongoing to identify her,
OL,11,Fso her next of kin can be notified.
OL,13,F"Detectives are also releasing details
OL,14,Fof her identity in the hope that
OL,15,Fsomeone will recognise her from the
OL,16,Ffollowing description.
OL,18,F"She is of slim build and has tanned
OL,19,Fskin.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774951543
OL,3,CPolice begin murder investigation as
OL,4,Cyoung women found dead on suburban
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,F"She is 5ft 2ins tall and believed to
OL,8,Fbe in her mid to late teens, with
OL,9,Fgreen eyes and brown hair with darker
OL,10,Froots and blonde ends. She also has
OL,11,Ffixed metal braces to her upper and
OL,12,Flower teeth."
OL,14,FTwo women aged 18, a man aged 20 and a
OL,15,Fboy aged 17 have all arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
