OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774951543
OL,3,CPolice begin murder investigation as
OL,4,Cyoung women found dead on suburban
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,8,FDetective Chief Superintendent Marc
OL,9,FBowes, said: "This is an extremely
OL,10,Fcomplex investigation where a young
OL,11,Fwoman has sadly lost her life.
OL,13,F"We are treating her death as murder
OL,14,Fand have arrested four people in
OL,15,Fconnection with it.
OL,17,F"Despite carrying out extensive
OL,18,Fenquiries throughout the course of
OL,19,Ftoday we have not yet been able to
OL,20,Fconfirm her identity.
OL,26,@qD@NOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774951543
OL,3,CPolice begin murder investigation as
OL,4,Cyoung women found dead on suburban
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,F"We hope by releasing these details
OL,8,Fthat someone will recognise who she is
OL,9,Fand come forward.
OL,11,F"I am also keen to speak to anyone who
OL,12,Fwas in the Kennerleigh Avenue area in
OL,13,Fthe early hours of this morning, or
OL,14,Fanyone who may have seen any
OL,15,Fsuspicious activity in the vicinity."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@eO]
